export const italianDishes = [
  {
    id: "pizza-margherita",
    title: "Pizza Margherita",
    image:
      "https://api.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/608636c956ec59063fecc3b46b4f1c7e8b0c5eff?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=b59f74ae8c9444f28ee33eff06842d33",
    price: "₹300",
    quantity: "8-inch",
    description: "Classic pizza with tomato, mozzarella, and basil",
    rating: 5,
    ingredients: ["Pizza base", "Tomato sauce", "Mozzarella", "Basil"],
    instructions: [
      "Spread sauce on base.",
      "Add cheese and basil.",
      "Bake at 220°C for 10–15 mins.",
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "classic-veg-burger",
    title: "Classic Veg Burger",
    image:
      "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/2209004079/cs/fotografie/classic-burger-on-a-wrapping-paper.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=om69xiD6iSPNLOfHKQQ909R6vVpnh-giGO9gBIY2XmQ=",
    price: "₹200",
    quantity: "1 burger",
    description: "Soft bun with crispy veg patty and fresh veggies",
    rating: 4.7,
    ingredients: ["Burger bun", "Veg patty", "Lettuce", "Tomato", "Cheese"],
    instructions: [
      "Toast the bun.",
      "Cook the patty.",
      "Assemble with veggies and sauce.",
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "veg-sushi-roll",
    title: "Veg Sushi Roll",
    image:
      "https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/sushi.jpg",
    price: "₹350",
    quantity: "6 pieces",
    description: "Delicate rolls filled with seasoned rice and vegetables",
    rating: 4.5,
    ingredients: ["Sushi rice", "Nori", "Cucumber", "Carrot", "Avocado"],
    instructions: [
      "Prepare and season the rice.",
      "Place fillings on nori.",
      "Roll tightly and slice.",
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "veggie-taco",
    title: "Veggie Taco",
    image:
      "https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/taco.jpg",
    price: "₹220",
    quantity: "2 tacos",
    description: "Tacos stuffed with spiced vegetables and beans",
    rating: 4.6,
    ingredients: ["Taco shells", "Beans", "Onion", "Capsicum", "Salsa"],
    instructions: [
      "Heat taco shells.",
      "Cook veggie filling.",
      "Fill tacos and top with salsa.",
    ],
  },
];
